Perfect for time-crunched, on-the-go lifestyles, the 5-Min Ampoule Sheet Mask gives you #FastAndSerious results in just 5 minutes! 💚

Carefully formulated to target three different key skin needs, the #5MinMasks are packed with all the goodness of skincare actives and natural origin ingredients! 🍉🍍🥬

Try them exclusively on @myntra & @myntrabeauty!

The New 5-Min Ampoule Masks are better for you & better for the planet!

Our formulas for each mask are vegan and the sheet masks themselves are too. Our sheet masks are made from two fibres, calcium alginate – which originates from natural origin Laminariales seaweed ethically sourced from beaches across Chile – and lyocell, that’s derived from sustainable wood. 

Are you curious to try these vegan masks?
You can get your hands on these exclusively on @myntra & @myntrabeauty! 💚

*vegan formula = no animal-derived ingredients or by-products
